ğŸ§‘â€ğŸ’» 5ï¸âƒ£ Compile & Run in VS Code
âœ… A. Configure Tomcat

In VS Code, press Ctrl+Shift+P â†’ Tomcat: Add Tomcat Server

Browse to your Tomcat installation folder.

The server will appear in the TOMCAT SERVERS panel (bottom left).

âœ… B. Deploy Project

Right-click on your CurrencyConverter folder â†’ Add to Tomcat Server.

VS Code will automatically deploy it.

âœ… C. Run the Project

Once deployed, right-click the project in Tomcat panel â†’ Start.
Then open your browser and go to:
ğŸ‘‰ http://localhost:8080/CurrencyConverter/index.jsp

You should see your Currency Converter running ğŸ‰

